There are some weeks that I get to take Blu to experience fun activities, and there are some busy weeks that we don’t get to do much and instead just stay home. 

I have gotten so many messages and advice from beautiful moms around not feeling guilty in these cases and just don’t try too hard. Motherhood is already full of it.

It’s okay if you don’t always play, it’s okay to not always stimulate, it’s okay to involve them in our daily activities. It’s okay.

So on the weekends that we get the opportunity to do something special, we love the outdoors, animals and spending time with our loved ones ♥️

——- 
Hay algunas semanas en las que llevo a Blu a experimentar actividades divertidas, y hay algunas semanas más ocupadas en las que no podemos hacer eso y, en cambio, nos quedamos en casa.

He recibido tantos mensajes y consejos de hermosas mamás sobre no sentirse culpable en estos casos y simplemente dejar que las cosas fluyan. La maternidad ya está llena de esos momentos.

No siempre se tiene que jugar, no siempre se tiene que estimular, a veces simplemente involucrarlos en nuestras actividades diarias es suficiente. Y está bien. 

Entonces, los fines de semana que tenemos la oportunidad de hacer algo especial, nos encanta el aire libre, los animales y pasar tiempo con nuestros seres queridos ♥️

On my Q&A I got asked a lot about under eyes. With jet-lag, Blu adapting to the new sleep schedule and work my under eyes have been talking loud and clear 😅 

These are 3 products I’ve been using lately to help with my dark circles:

- @lorealparis eye serum: helps to visibly brighten dark circles. 

- @olehenriksen eye cream: Smoothes skin texture and hydrates.

- @garnierusa SkinActive Tinted Eye Roller: I used this instead of using concealer. It brightens and awakens the eye with a makeup effect.

ps: I don’t necessarily use them together, but there are days when it is necessary 🤣

——————

En mi Q&A, me preguntaron mucho sobre las ojeras. Con el jet-lag, Blu adaptándose al nuevo horario de sueño y trabajo, mis ojos han estado hablando alto y claro 😅

Estos son 3 productos que he estado usando últimamente para ayudar con mis ojeras:

- @lorealparis eye serum: ayuda a iluminar visiblemente las ojeras y a rellenar las líneas de los ojos

- Crema para ojos: Suaviza la textura de la piel e hidrata

- Garnier SkinActive Tinted Eye Roller: Uso esto en lugar de usar corrector. Ilumina y despierta la mirada con efecto maquillaje.

P.D: no necesariamente los uso juntos, pero hay días que es necesario 🤣

I get comments like these all the time, and while I’m incredibly grateful. I always think about the Sharon from the past that was looking for answers and didn’t know what was happening. That Sharon that was going through postpartum, and was navigating her “new body.”

I always shared my love for skincare and wellness, but I never shared a picture of why. This is why. And I’m glad I can share now my experience with it all, from a different place not only, physically, but mentally.

I’m proud of that Sharon and I should have been easier on her because she deserved it.

If you want to know more about my skin journey and what I did to arrive here, check out my last video on my YouTube channel, link on my bio. 🤍

These three years have been the most beautiful of my life. I feel like it was yesterday that you arrived and at the same time I feel like I’ve had you all my life. I don’t know how I lived before you. Thank you for being so special and choosing me as your mom. I promise to try to be the best mom I can be for you. I love you, forever my angel Blu.
Thank you @gianlucavacchi for giving me the most beautiful gift of my life. We are so lucky to have you. I couldn’t have choosen a better father, I’m so proud of the wonderful daddy you are. We love you. ♥️

A mi princesa, 
Estos tres años han sido los más hermosos de mi vida. Siento que fue ayer que llegaste y al mismo tiempo siento que te he tenido toda mi vida. No se como vivía antes de ti.
